downloadTitle: Guide for IT Pros for Microsoft Project Server 2010 Beta
downloadDescription: Contains information about how to deploy and use Microsoft Project Server 2010 Beta.
detailsSection: This document supports a preliminary release of Microsoft Project Server 2010 Beta. The content in the book covers information about how to install, configure, and upgrade to Project Server 2010 Beta.
installInstructionSection:
1. Click the Download button in the upper right corner of this page to start the download.
  2. Click Save or Save this program to disk.
  3. Find the file on your hard disk and double-click it to open it.
